at least once or twice by now.

51
00:02:15,489 --> 00:02:16,489
But the point is,

52
00:02:16,489 --> 00:02:19,010
Meng is not only the CFO of Huawei.

53
00:02:19,010 --> 00:02:23,340
She’s also the daughter of Huawei’s founder,
Ren Zhengfei.

54
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:26,480
He’s worth 3.2 billion dollars.

55
00:02:26,489 --> 00:02:31,250
And he’s a former officer of the People’s
Liberation Army.

56
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:34,489
That makes her not just an heiress to the
Huawei empire,

57
00:02:34,489 --> 00:02:37,519
but potentially a key figure in the Chinese
Communist Party’s

58
00:02:37,519 --> 00:02:39,970
shady relationship with Huawei.

59
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:43,409
Huawei has faced accusations of conducting
espionage

60
