“I can assure everyone that

121
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:23,160
we are a country of an independent judiciary

122
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:27,580
and the appropriate authorities took the decisions
in this case

123
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:30,760
without any political involvement or interference,

124
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,720
