decision

154
00:06:51,770 --> 00:06:53,729
because we respect the independence

155
00:06:53,729 --> 00:06:55,280
of our judicial processes.”

156
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:58,050
Yeah, Canada is not letting her go.

157
00:06:58,050 --> 00:06:59,050
And you know,

158
00:06:59,050 --> 00:07:01,470
as much as I like to make fun of Canada and
Justin Trudeau—

159
00:07:01,470 --> 00:07:04,060
